wdi-GC.AST.TOTL.CN.def: Net acquisition of government financial assets includes domestic and foreign financial claims, SDRs, and gold bullion held by monetary authorities as a reserve asset. The net acquisition of financial assets should be offset by the net incurrence of liabilities.
wdi-GC.AST.TOTL.CN.name: Net acquisition of financial assets
wdi-GC.AST.TOTL.CN.source: International Monetary Fund, Government Finance Statistics Yearbook and data files.
